column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, s.ra, s.dec, s.class, s.subClass, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning,s.bestObjID, s.specObjID, g.oiii_flux FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN SpecObj s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN GalSpecLine AS g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
